# AI Assistant Guidelines & Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React
- Architecture/State: Redux
- Testing: Unit and widget testing

## Code Style & Conventions
- Maintain a clean, modular structure following the designated architecture patterns.
- Prefer explicit types over inferred types where applicable.
- Write self-documenting code with concise inline comments for complex logic.

## Build and Test Commands
- Development command: npm run dev
- Test command: npm test
- Code generation/Linting: 